{"tid":1627793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要\b] 手足們，我哋嘅行動一定要有呢樣野！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:19:51.000Z","uid":47541,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11445a28f876ecafa1b95e586cfa30afb65bf6fe","tid":1627793,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"(頭先個post有排版問題，重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n就係「正當性」！<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得我哋嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">行動背後必須有正當性</span>，未必真係話要有規條去守，而係每個行動背後都需要有正當嘅理據。<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，喺「當獨裁成為事實，革命就是義務」下，有<span style=\"color: red;\">正當性嘅目標就係政權、政權嘅工具</span>（警察、黨鐵）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而支持政府嘅藍色公司／人，固然係討厭，但除非佢地對我地完成目標有威脅（如攻擊手足），否則我哋亦冇必要去出擊佢地，更理想通過裝飾／罷買／和你shop作為表態</span>，表示我方同佢地恥與為伍，但同時留有空間，歡迎佢地改邪歸正。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，如果仲有時間都希望大家可以花少少時間睇一睇以下幾個post：<br />\n<br />\n1.［勇武和理非大和解］終極行動守則上線了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kkRdcrW\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kkRdcrW</a><br />\n- 以武制暴唔係問題，但要<span style=\"color: red;\">緊記我哋係戰鬥人員，唔係暴徒</span>，唔好用道德直覺判斷邊個抵打，武力要用得其所。準則包括：唔好打平民（包括路過好嘈好煩、持唔同意見、但無戰鬥能力既人）、醫護人員、記者、已經投降嘅人；容許受影響嘅所有人（不論陣營）接受人道支援（包括急救）。<br />\n<br />\n2. 經過今晚有幾樣嘢真係唔好再做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624134</a><br />\n- 內文已經好簡結：不要成立臨時政府，提倡港獨、不要鳩打非暴力既藍絲/蝗國人、不要幫零售型藍絲/中資商店裝修<br />\n- 延伸閱讀：<span style=\"color: red;\">四大分類：黑裝修，紅裝飾，藍罷買，黃幫襯</span>（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624486）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624486）</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 梁天琦給香港人的信（29/7/19）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381054</a><br />\n- 唔需多解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n最後，重申「不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責」，尊重大家決定，咩都好我地都會盡力用文宣cover對外解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7a16f91e3cf7e2ffb82ffdf644e720a45ca3d9","tid":1627793,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:55:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府越想淡化<br />\n我地越要推<br />\n毋忘721 831</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P10Kbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P10Kbc.jpg&h=66ce219c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gDivRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gDivRd.jpg&h=9e847180&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZFHXwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZFHXwd.jpg&h=68a9a8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKXZZKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKXZZKz.jpg&h=933e09df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a56fbbabc5ff29a7cb454acdd1121e34a39e12f","tid":1627793,"uid":47541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JC5XMup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJC5XMup.jpg&h=f5a082b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca3591b4a228ce9d8b6f40fddf54b19c5560eb1","tid":1627793,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"見你咁有誠意幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26e14dfb253763095765fbbdedf1dafa7c22f36","tid":1627793,"uid":47541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3RXLaWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3RXLaWy.jpg&h=96f3391d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b37b043345d5284e2760a23222481d8f20ee2c6","tid":1627793,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n1／20"},{"pid":"2932661bdeac367b625e656e20e5899f63005